      "text": "Apple on Thursday rolled out security updates [https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201222 https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT201222] to iOS, iPadOS, macOS, tvOS, watchOS, and the Safari web browser to address three new zero-day flaws that it said are being actively exploited in the wild."
